* PyCOBOL Test Case 1: CLEAN CODE (No Errors)
* Demonstrates all valid token types recognized by the lexer

IDENTIFICATION DIVISION
PROGRAM-ID: StudentGrading
AUTHOR: CS Student
DATE-WRITTEN: 2026-05-04

DATA DIVISION
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION
    01 student_name     PIC A(30)
    01 marks            PIC 9(3)
    01 percentage       PIC 9(3)V99
    01 grade            PIC A(2)

PROCEDURE DIVISION

# Initialize student data
student_name = "Ali Ahmed"
marks = 450
percentage = 90.50

# COBOL-style computation
COMPUTE percentage = marks / 500 * 100

# Python-style control flow with COBOL operations
if percentage >= 90:
    grade = "A+"
    DISPLAY "Excellent performance!"
elif percentage >= 80:
    grade = "A"
    DISPLAY "Good job!"
elif percentage >= 70:
    grade = "B"
else:
    grade = "C"

# Loop through subjects
for i in range(5):
    DISPLAY "Subject " i " processed"

# Final output
DISPLAY "Student : " student_name
DISPLAY "Marks   : " marks
DISPLAY "Grade   : " grade

STOP RUN
